Opsonin Pharma Limited is a pharmaceutical company in Bangladesh which was established in 1956. Accoriding to an IMS Health (Intercontinental Marketing Services, Health) report, Opsonin Pharma Limited is the 4th largest pharmaceutical company in Bangladesh in terms of sales.
Sister concerns include Opsosaline Ltd, Global Capsules Ltd, Global Heavy Chemicals Ltd, and Jokky Garments Ltd.
